      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Maya_InteractiveDenoiser_RenderMan.JPG\" width=\"814\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544542924/Maya_InteractiveDenoiser_RenderMan.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431590049&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=814&amp;height=331\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544542924/Maya_InteractiveDenoiser_RenderMan.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431590049&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"919\" data-width=\"2255\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544542942\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Maya_InteractiveDenoiser_RenderMan.JPG\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544542924\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"279154b4-4480-4c09-a6b4-f019eba363c5\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544542924/Maya_InteractiveDenoiser_RenderMan.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431590049&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1628&amp;height=662 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544542924/Maya_InteractiveDenoiser_RenderMan.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431590049&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=814&amp;height=331 1x\"></span><p>To activate the RfM Interactive Denoiser, fire up a viewport render and select the Denoiser icon</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Maya_InteractiveDenoiser_viewport_RenderMan.jpg\" width=\"832\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544542924/Maya_InteractiveDenoiser_viewport_RenderMan.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431590049&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=670&amp;height=44\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544542924/Maya_InteractiveDenoiser_viewport_RenderMan.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431590049&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"44\" data-width=\"670\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544542936\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Maya_InteractiveDenoiser_viewport_RenderMan.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544542924\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"461dcc88-29fb-4f62-b0fb-603e43d05812\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544542924/Maya_InteractiveDenoiser_viewport_RenderMan.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431590049&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=670&amp;height=44 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544542924/Maya_InteractiveDenoiser_viewport_RenderMan.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431590049&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=670&amp;height=44 1x\"></span><p>  </p><hr/><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Maya_InteractiveDenoiser_panel_RenderMan.JPG\" width=\"832\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544542924/Maya_InteractiveDenoiser_panel_RenderMan.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431590049&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=832&amp;height=399\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544542924/Maya_InteractiveDenoiser_panel_RenderMan.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431590049&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"694\" data-width=\"1445\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544542939\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Maya_InteractiveDenoiser_panel_RenderMan.JPG\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544542924\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"8492d745-6066-484b-baf3-62d8aa10448d\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544542924/Maya_InteractiveDenoiser_panel_RenderMan.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431590049&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1445&amp;height=694 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544542924/Maya_InteractiveDenoiser_panel_RenderMan.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431590049&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=832&amp;height=399 1x\"></span><p /><p><strong>Cheap First Pass</strong><br/>If checked, the first pass will use a cheaper (slightly faster but lower quality) heuristic.</p><p>This can be useful if rendering something that is converging very quickly and you want to prioritize getting a denoised result faster.</p><p><strong>Min Samples</strong><br/>The minimum number of average samples per bucket before the interactive denoiser runs for the first time.  Changing this preference requires the render to be restarted for this option to be respected</p><p><strong>Interval</strong><br/>The time interval in between denoise runs (in seconds)</p><p /><p /><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"cd2ad515-4d0d-4871-9868-99d03e793306\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>Note : At this time, the interactive denoiser works with RIS</p></div></div><div class=\"panel conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"\" data-macro-name=\"panel\" style=\"background-color: #EAE6FF;border-color: #998DD9;border-width: 1px;\"><div class=\"panelContent\" style=\"background-color: #EAE6FF;\">\n<p>Note : To enhance interactivity when working on asset lookdev, try increasing the min samples to 8-10 and reduce back down to 2 - 4 when working on a larger scene.</p>\n</div></div><p />"
    }
